= 0 C.E. --- Guild District #emph[(Special)] <guild-district-special>
#link("#")[← Buildings & Wonders]

== Purpose <purpose>

In thriving cities, production districts often grew around central coordination points where labor, tools, and transport routes converged. By organizing extraction sites more efficiently, the city could significantly increase the output of its surrounding lands.

The Guild District acts as a central command hub that optimizes the work of your city's labor force and production facilities.

Once constructed, the Guild District increases the production of all primary resources in the city: wood, stone, metal, and food.

~ Strategic focus: #strong[Economic growth]
